txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: A collection of grey goo from the insects surrounding Echad Candelleth. All items should be delivered to Bainthir at the camp.
'Know that this will be used well. Thank you.'

'The Men who are here need lessons, and I have need of items that will teach them such a lesson. If you can collect the filth, carapaces, and goo from the insects in the area, it would be well recovered.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Grey Goo
Bainthir, an Elf at the camp of Echad Candelleth, is awaiting a delivery of grey goo.
Deliver the grey goo to Bainthir at Echad Candelleth in the Trollshaws
You have accepted a task to collect grey goo from the insects surrounding Echad Candelleth. You are to deliver the items to Bainthir at the camp.
Wanted: A collection of grey goo from the insects surrounding Echad Candelleth.
